title: Daz3d FWSA Liam HD for Michael 7
description:
Liam is a high quality character for Michael 7.

The head and body for Liam are uniquely custom sculpted in Zbrush, and the skin was created using high quality photo references for depth and detail. He also comes with custom sculpted nipples that will apply when the main morph dials are applied.

So whether you're looking for a sexy young man, a cool Goth, a rock star, or the boy next door... Liam will be perfect for all renders.


Compatible Figures: Genesis 3 Male
